 (a^b)^{c+1}=(a^b)^c\cdot a^b=a^{bc}\cdot a^b=a^{bc+b}=a^{b(c+1)} 
 (a^b)^c=\frac{1}{(a^b)^d}=\frac{1}{a^{bd}}=\frac{1}{a^{-bc}}=a^{bc} 
